To setup:
=========


1. Install the Haskell Platform (http://hackage.haskell.org/platform/)
2. Install Pandoc: `cabal install pandoc`
3. Install Hakyll: `cabal install hakyll`

To build the site:
==================

$ rm -r out
$ ./generate.sh


To test the site:
=================

$ ./serve.sh
$ open http://localhost:8000/
